{"word":"παρενθήκη","slug":"παρενθήκη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n79386\" key=\"parenqh/kh\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">παρεν-θήκη</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n79386.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">something put in beside, addition</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοιήνδε . . παρενθήκην ἐποιήσατο</foreign>, of works undertaken <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in completion of others</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.186</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παρενθήκην ἔχρησε ἐς Μιλησίους</foreign> delivered an oracle <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by way of parenthesis</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.19</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῦ λόγου π. ποιεέσκετο τήνδε, ὡς</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.5</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:171\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">171</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑτέρας τοῦ πολέμου π. ἐποιεῖτο</foreign> undertook other <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">business in the intervals of</tr_> the war, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg045:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pomp.\">Pomp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. ὄψου,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">παροψώνημα</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:6:56\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.56</biblScope> </bibl> ; of a remedy <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">interposed</tr_> in a difficult situation, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2200.tlg004:59:95\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lib.\">Lib.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">59.95</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n79386.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">smaller wares taken as an addition to the cargo</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ἐμπορία</foreign>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.151e</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:1:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.99</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}